title: Cardinals created by Innocent VIII
text: <a href="Pope%20Innocent%20VIII">Pope Innocent VIII</a> (r. 1484–1492) created eight new <a href="Cardinal%20%28Catholicism%29">cardinals</a> in one <a href="Papal%20consistory">consistory</a> on 9 March 1489, although the names of two of them were published only after his death:
